StarFlier::
"Knock it out? Oh yeah. Sure. I can stun it. My tail is fully 
equipped with a stun halo.  My parents didn't want me killing my 
friends with a sharp tail like thiers. So I got a stun halo. But I 
think I had more fun with it that I would ever have had with a sharp 
spiked tail anyway."  She worked very careful and with great skill 
removing the final layer of the coccoon.  She lifted her tail near 
the bot's head. "If it so much as twitches funny, I'll just put it 
back to sleep. See, nothing to worry about."
